div.div:
Ghi ch
1a. Khi container vo n cng khai bo thng tin container vi CMS. CMS s pub thng tin container n Kafka.
1b. OPS core sub Thng tin container a vo b Filter tm v tr container ph hp.
2a. V tr container c OPS core pub n Kafka.
2b. Service CMS sub v tr container ri lu trong database (2c). H thng CMS s truy xut khi cn.
3a. Khi CMS bm gi gate-in th CMS s pub status ca s Container cn pht lnh.
3b. OPS core sub Status ca s container cn pht lnh.
4a. OPS core pub lnh lm hng thuc v 1 phng tin c th n Kafka.
4b. OPS-Web-Mobile sub lnh lm hng v a ln hng i.
5a. Khi lm hng thnh cng OPS-Web-Mobile pub v tr container trn bi.
5b. OPS core sub v tr container trn bi ri cp nht vo cc Service cn thit.
6a. CMS pub lnh hy lm hng cho container no .
6b. OPS core sub lnh hy lm hng ca 1 container no . Nu lnh lm hng c OPS-Web-Mobile cp nht v tr container trn bi th xem nh lnh hy tht bi, ngc li phi kim tra tip.
7.1a. OPS core pub trng thi hy tht bi ca lnh hy lm hng n Kafka.
7.1b. CMS sub trng thi hy lnh lm hng (Hy tht bi) v cp nht li h thng ca mnh.
7.2a OPS core pub trng thi hy thnh cng ca lnh hy lm hng n Kafka.
7.2b OPS-Web-Mobile sub trng thi hy lm hng. Nu container cn hy cn nm trong hng i th xa (Hoc cp nht trng thi Hy).
8a. OPS-Web-Mobile pub trng thi hy lm hng Thnh cng cho Kafka.
8b. OPS core sub Trng thi hy lm hng Thnh cng vo h thng.
9a. OPS core pub Trng thi hy lm hng Thnh cng cho Kafka.
9b. CMS sub Trng thi hy lm hng Thnh cng ri cp nht li vo h thng ca mnh.
